The beach



On the way from Madonna Inn to Big Sur, we stopped for the morning at Moonstone Beach, near Cambria at the south end of the Big Sur coast.
This shot was taken looking south from near the middle of the beach.
Taken Sunday, June 24, 2001, 11:36:53am.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 962kb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/1000s @ F4.5, ISO 100, 211mm
PS6 Curves 25:0 - 130:175 - 220:255, R 0:0 - 255:240, Unsharp Mask 2.0 50%
